headline: Is State Street (STT) Still Attractive After A 36.9% Share Price Gain?
summary: If you are wondering whether State Street's share price still offers value after a solid run, this article walks through the key numbers that matter for you. Over the last year the stock has returned 36.9%, with a 3.1% gain over the past week, a 0.7% decline over the last 30 days, and a 2.3% return year to date. This may signal that expectations and perceived risk are shifting. Recent coverage of State Street has focused on its role as a major custody bank and asset servicer, and how market...
